This paper discusses boosting algorithms for convex optimization, which is a common topic in machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also includes experimental results related to computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE), which further support these categories.
